{"tid":731158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[怕你放蛇咬]人行馬駿：500億美元貿易戰對中國經濟影響有限 已基本被市場消化","createTime":"2018-07-06T03:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T03:47:12.000Z","uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d957e71f1f33832bd168de01eb775dc6e2e75a9","tid":731158,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"據《新華社》引述人民銀行貨幣政策委員會委員、清華大學金融與發展研究中心主任馬駿表示，中美之間500億美元規模的貿易戰對中國經濟的影響有限，對經濟、行業和企業的影響基本上已經被消化，故未必會對資本市場和匯率有太大的影響。<br />\n<br />\n馬駿認為，對某些受到影響相對較大的行業，有關方面還會考慮必要的對沖措施來降低貿易戰帶來的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n據測算，與基準情景(即沒有貿易戰情景)相比，500億美元規模的貿易戰會使中國的GDP增速放緩0.2個百分點。該估計已充分考慮了出口減少對其它相關行業的第二輪、第三輪影響<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.882242/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.882242%2F2&d=c9KDJrwBTBNzjMKrMG0jmjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=81404145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.882242/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c698a357f5f1696cd77c44f1d154bceb89605dc","tid":731158,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"OK，加多4500億美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732984a37e40e65f55ff22d916ff7812fec2e37b","tid":731158,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T03:47:12.000Z","msg":"中或最贏"}]}